questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The number of&amp;nbsp;rural people who are either farmers or rich but NOT both is shown below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/21/10/F1_Aprajita_Ravi_22.10.21_D38.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 356px; height: 117px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

